quote><br />\n<br />\n唔明掃二維碼有咩咁「先進」<br />\n<br />\n其實八達通解決到保安問題用其他方式access 張卡戶口唔係問題（例如用手機支付）</blockquote><br />\n開口埋口先進<br />\n喺個爛鬼qr code加兩筆已經搞死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a0d46054f3ad298beb552d40d8475b0eb47bee","tid":452376,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d6916bbe7f8125c09c34b12ff3deb2ec7a556fc","tid":452376,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"858d8044a290c77ca9909ed334f3820734f50461","tid":452376,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落後？邊撚度落後？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好快就有政府電視廣告<br />\n<br />\n不斷LOOP話八仔「落後」, 支那寶掃CODE入密碼係「先進」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明掃二維碼有咩咁「先進」<br />\n<br />\n其實八達通解決到保安問題用其他方式access 張卡戶口唔係問題（例如用手機支付）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啪張卡實在係太快太方便, 呢個就係8仔先進既地方<br />\n你根本完全唔會想經手機去用八仔比錢<br />\n<br />\n相反, 經手機用信用卡比錢, 係方便過快過拿張卡去碌 + 等資料傳送 + 簽名<br />\n所以手機支付只會搶奪信用卡支付, 而唔係8仔<br />\n<br />\n支那寶以8仔為假想敵, 根本策略上就係ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAPPLE PAY DEMO都唔係以oyster card做假想敵, 係用信用卡<br />\n支那人根本都分唔到小額快速支付 同 大額電子支付 係兩個唔同領域<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ExcCyS1ZH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5ExcCyS1ZH8&d=AGvHFC3Ye9q1nZzXwKH0%2F1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=1f9b43f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ExcCyS1ZH8</a>"},{"pid":"cfc880fbbe22affff61c7d357835849ef2594a42","tid":452376,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e63ab2b750c1922319fd7f8c27f07f671a4f8872","tid":452376,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落後